title: Lego has gone boldly where they have never gone before with their first-ever Star Trek set, and it's back in stock with a free gift!
description: The 3,600-piece Lego Icons Star Trek USS Enterprise is Lego's first-ever Star Trek set, and you get a free gift when you purchase it before Christmas eve.
